# Contents/ is populated by scripts/Build-Release.ps1 from
# src/Acd.Mcp/bin/Release/. The build outputs (Acd.Mcp.dll + transitive
# deps such as Acd.Mcp.Api.dll, Acd.Mcp.Batch.dll, AvalonEdit.dll,
# CommunityToolkit.Mvvm.dll, and the Roslyn scripting DLLs) end up here.
#
# This .gitkeep keeps the folder shape in source control so the bundle
# layout is reviewable. The actual binaries are never committed — they
# come from a Release build on a machine with AutoCAD 2025 installed
# (because Acd.Mcp.dll references AutoCAD's managed APIs at compile
# time).
